text: Ra uniharumadhyebatai e'uta samuhale bhan'yoh ki he madinavalaharu! Yaham timro nimti tha'um chaina, tasartha pharkihala, ra unako e'uta arko samuhale paigambarasita yo bhanera jane anumati mamgna thalyo ki ‘‘hamra ghara asuraksita chan’’. Yadyapi tiniharu khulla ra asuraksita thi'enan, tara uniharu ta kevala bhagna cahanthe
